snippet.title: SpellForce: Conquest of Eo - Weaver's Realms | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
SpellForce: Conquest of Eo - Weaver's Realms is OUT NOW!

Endless possibilities await… you just have to pierce the veil.

Learn to harness the power of dreams and create countless realms with the mere click of a button in the upcoming expansion for SpellForce: Conquest of Eo, a turn-based fantasy epic set in the world of SpellForce.

Discord: https://discord.gg/spellforce
